examples.en: He was very discreet, only saying what was necessary.
With a discreet gesture, she signalled to her husband that she was ready to leave the party.
The lovers met discreetly for the purposes of sexual congress.
She does not allow her young daughter to watch any films in which lovemaking is shown, however discreetly.
The lady discreetly whispered that she would be ready after a moment in the cloakroom.
I sent for the sergeant of the platoon both men were in and asked him to try to find out discreetly what lay behind this.
